recolytic,is,a,recommendation,engine,exposed,as,a,service,with,its,rich,personalization,framework,it,helps,users,discover,the,best,recommendation,strategies,for,their,business,This,API,collects,user,actions,such,as,likes,ratings,and,visits,It,will,provide,recommendation,strategies,based,on,these,actions,and,measure,the,performance,based,on,strategy,and,location